data.description: Fantastic opportunity to live, renovate or build your dream home in the highly desirable Dilworth neighborhood. Lockhart Drive is one of the most popular and sought after streets in all of Dilworth and only a short stroll away from Freedom Park, Sugar Creek Greenway, Atrium Main and all great restaurants and shops along East Blvd. This brick ranch home features 3-bedrooms 2 full baths with hardwood floors mostly throughout. There is also a large unheated sunroom and deck overlooking the backyard. In addition to the home, there is a large two car garage and a small shed/workshop on the property. This is an absolutely beautiful 0.33-acre lot with large majestic oaks and a private fenced yard. This prime location is convenient to just about everything Charlotte has to offer. Seller wishes to sell the home AS-IS in it's current condition.
